GQI model:

Create Session Command:
  sessionId: 10 bytes (Client)
  incomingPrgmNmbr
  outgoingPrgmNmbr
  inputPortNmbr
  sessionRate
  multicast (boolean)
  inputDestMcastIpAddr
  inputDestUpdPort
  inputSrcIpAddress[3]
  noPidRemapping

Delete Session Command:
  sessionId

Query Sessions Command:
  outputPortNmbr

Query Sessions Response:
  outputPortNmbr
  sessionId[]

Query Session Info Command:
  outputPortNmbr
  sessionId

Query Session Info Response
  sessionId
  incomingPrgmNmbr
  outgoingPrgmNmbr
  inputPortNmbr
  outputPortNmbr
  sessionRate
  inputPsiDetected
  packetsDetected
  programPmt[1024]
  multicast
  inputDestMcastIpAddr
  inputDestUdpPort
  soruceIpAddress[3]
  noPidRemapping

Create Shell Session Group Command:
  outputPortNmbr
  sessionId[32]
  groupRate
  inputPortNmbr

Create Shell Session Group Response:
  groupSessionStatus[32]

Delete Shell Session Group Command:
  outputPortNmbr
  sessionId[32]

Delete Shell Session Group Response:
  groupSessionStatus[32]


Bind Request:
  sessionId
  outputPgmNmbr
  inputPgmNmbr
  overrideBindingFlag
  pgmBandwidth
  destIpAddr
  destUdpPort
  sourceIpAddr[3]
  noPidRemapping

Unbind Request:
  sessionId

Query Bindings Command:

Query Bindings Response:
  sessionId[1024]

Query Binding Info Command:
  sessionId

Query Bind Info Response:
  sessionId
  outputPgmNmbr
  inputPgmNmbr
  overrideBindingFlag
  pgmBandwidth
  destIpAddr
  sourceIpAddr[3]
  noPidRemapping


