NGOD model:

VOD: unicast
  dest IP, dest UDP
  src IP, src UDP
  qam channel
  out prog num
  bandwidth
  jitterBuffer


SDV: multicast
  qam channel
  out prog num
  bandwidth
  For each source:
    bandwidth
    src IP
    group IP
    dst port
    in prog num
    (IP for IGMP join)


